This page collects material related to 

* [[Georg Hegel]]

  _Lectures on the History of Philosophy_

  ([German hypertext](http://hegel.abcphil.de/html/inhaltsverzeichnis.html), [English hypertext](https://www.marxists.org/reference/archive/hegel/works/hp/hpconten.htm))

on the history of [[philosophy]], presented, essentially, as a progression of philosophical systems ([philosophy as development](#AufeinanderfolgeDerSysteme)) of the _world spirit_ eventually converging ([result](#BisHierher)) to Hegel's own _[[Science of Logic]]_ .

